Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.37,0:00:06.16,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Andate a fare compere per il festival sportivo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:07.98,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Mi ricorda i vecchi tempi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.41,0:00:13.23,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sarò in grado di fare da guida come si deve?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:17.25,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,In effetti... è un centro commerciale piuttosto grande.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:21.99,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Comunque non vedo l'ora.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:24.59,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Sei in tempo per prendere l'autobus?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:25.24,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Decisamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:27.84,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Hai controllato bene gli orari del weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.58,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Vado a leggerli ancora una volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:30.95,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Ehi, ehi! Non muoverti!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:32.36,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hai ragione...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:34.77,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Vado a prenderteli io!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:37.26,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sono sulla credenza in soggiorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:41.95,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Bene. Ecco fatto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:48.56,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:25.90,italicstop,Bus Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,Prossima fermata...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:31.00,italicstop,Bus Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,Amatsumiko. Amatsumiko.
